## Quick Reference

```bash
# Show all commands
lists

# Audit dependencies
supplier:audit

# Create new agent
creator:agent my-agent --type sw-engineer

# Review code
dev:review src/main.go

# Memory management
memory:save
memory:recall authentication

# Pipeline execution
pipeline:list
pipeline:run code-review --input file_path=src/main.go

# Override intent detection
@golang-expert review this
```
